---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 301
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Necessity of Submission
By: St Ignatius of Antioch
---
Respect the bishop as a type of God, and the presbyters as the council
of God and the college of the Apostles. Apart from these there is not
even the name of a Church.
